    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Marii profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i ai religiilor, au fost totdeauna la ivirea lor dispre<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ui<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i respin<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de oameni. <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i ei <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i urma<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ii lor cei mai vechi, au primit smerit pe spate loviturile asupritorilor <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i-au jertfit via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i avutul pe c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rarea lui Dumnezeu. Chiar <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n zilele noastre, a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a s-a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mplat. De la 1844 A.D. multe mii de B<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>bii <text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span> din Persia au suferit o moarte crud<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, pentru credin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a lor; <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i mai mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i au suferit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nchisoare, surghiun, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cie <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i degradare. Ultima mare religie a fost „botezat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cu s<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nge” <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:sp