t:span>rat <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i un sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci orice lucru alc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tuit din p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rticele, fie individual, fie colectiv, trebuie neap<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se destrame <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rticele; singura deosebire e c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> unele se f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>eaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> repede, iar altele mai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncet, dar e cu neputin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> ca un lucru compus, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu fie <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n cursul timpului, descompus”. - R<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>spunsuri la c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>teva <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntreb<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri, p. 209.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P20">Originea omului.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>e<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rerea biologului care g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>se<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te pentru trupul omenesc, o origine, ce se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntinde <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n dezvoltarea spe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ei, p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> la milioane de ani <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>napoi. Trupul omenesc ni se arat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ca, ivindu-se sub o form<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> foarte simpl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, aproape f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsemn<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tate <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i apoi dezvolt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndu-se epoc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> epoc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-un <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ir de genera<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii, nespus de lung, ajung<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd din ce <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ce mai complex, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i din ce <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ce mai bine organizat, p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ajunge starea omului de azi. Fiece trup omenesc individual, se <text:soft-page-break/>dezvolt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> trec<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd printr-o serie asem<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toare de st<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri, de la o boab<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> mic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> gelatinoas<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de materie, p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> la forma omului, deplin dezvoltat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> acesta e adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rul pentru individ, ceea ce nimeni nu t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duie<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te, de ce-<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nchipuie c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> e o jignire a demnit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii umane, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> credem <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-o dezvoltare asem<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toare, a speciei <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntregi?</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T21">Asta e cu totul altceva dec</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">â</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">t crede, c</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21"> omul se coboar</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21"> din maimu</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">þã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">.</text:span> Embrionul uman, poate la un moment oarecare s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> semene cu un pe<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te, cu <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>not<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toare <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i coad<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, dar nu e pe<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te. E un embrion uman. Astfel <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i specia uman<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, a putut <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n diferite epoci, ale lugei ei dezvolt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fi sem<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>nat la aspect cu diferite specii de animale inferioare, dar totdeauna a fost tot specia uman<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nzestrat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cu misterioasa putere ascuns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de a se dezvolta p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> la <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntruchiparea omului, a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a cum o cunoa<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tem azi, ba mai mult <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, de a se dezvolta <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n viitor, n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>jduim, p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> la o form<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i mai des<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>v<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce spune ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„E un lucru sigur c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, globul terestru, nu a luat fiin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> de la <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceput, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n forma lui de azi, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a trecut treptat prin felurite faze, p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpodobeasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cu des<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>v<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>irea lui de acum.. Omul, la <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceputul existen<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ei lui, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntecele p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntului, ca <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i embrionul din p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntecele mamei, a crescut <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i s-a dezvoltat treptat, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a trecut de la o form<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> la alta, p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> s-a ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tat <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n frumuse<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ea <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i des<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>v<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>irea, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ria <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i puterea de azi. E lucru sigur c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> la <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceput, nu era <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nzestrat cu at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ta farmec, at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>tea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>iri, at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ta ml<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>dire, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> numai cu <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncetul a dob<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndit aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nf<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>i<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>are a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a de chipe<text:span text:style-name="T5">ºã</text:span>, de ademenitoare <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de pl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cut<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>... Via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a omului pe acest p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, de la <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceputul ei, p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ajung<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> la starea, la dezvoltarea <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i la <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nf<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>i<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>area de azi, a d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>inuit de bun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> seam<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, mult<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> vreme.. dar omul, chiar de la <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceputul existen<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ei lui, a fost o specie deosebit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Chiar dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> admitem c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> exist<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n corpul omului) <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i acum urmele unor organe, care au disp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rut, aceasta nu e o dovad<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> specia n-ar fi fost de la <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceput aceea<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i deosebit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de altele. Cel mult, poate dovedi, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> chipul, forma <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i organele omului, au prop<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>it. Omul a fost totdeauna o specie deosebit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, om, iar nu anima.” - R<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>spunsuri la c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>teva <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntreb<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri, pg. 211-214.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce spune ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, despre povestea lui Adam <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a Evei:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> lu<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> povestire <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elesul ei v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>dit, potrivit cu t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cirea dat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de popor <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeob<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te, e <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r nemaipomenit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Omul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nzestrat cu judecat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, nu poate s-o primeasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, s-o afirme, sau s-o <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nchipuiasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>; c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci o asemenea or<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nduire, astfel de am<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>nunte, asemenea convorbiri <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i mustr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri, sunt departe de ce ar putea face o fiin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> cu judecat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, cu at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t mai mult Divinitatea - acea Divinitate care a f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>urit acest nem<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rginit univers, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n form<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> lui at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t de des<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>v<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i numero<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ii s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>i locuitori cu ne<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nchipuit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> chibzuial<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, putere <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i me<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ug...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">A<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>adar, povestea lui Adam <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a Evei, care au m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ncat din rodul oprit <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i au fost <text:soft-page-break/>goni<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i din Rai, trebuie socotit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> numai caun simbol. Cuprinde mistere divine <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i nem<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rginite <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elesuri, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i poate fi l<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>murit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n minunate chipuri”. - R<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>spunsuri la c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>teva <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntreb<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri, p.140.</text:p>
