    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþã</text:span>turile Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>, cu privire la trup <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i la suflet, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i la via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a de dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> moarte, sunt <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n deplin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> armonie cu rezultatul cercet<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rilor asupra problemelor pshice. Ele ne <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nva<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>, dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cum am mai v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zut, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> moartea nu e dec<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t o nou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> na<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tere, - m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntuirea din c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ele trupului, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-o via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> mai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nalt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> progresul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a de apoi, n-are margini. S-au adunat treptat un mare num<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r de dovezi <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tiin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ifice, care dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rerea unor cercet<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tori nep<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rtinitori, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nzestra<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i cu mult sim<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span> critic, ne <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndrept<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>esc cu prisosin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> afirm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n mod net<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duit c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> exist<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> o via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> moarte - c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> „sufletul” con<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tient <text:span text:style-name="T5">îº</text:span>i urmeaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> moarte, via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i activitatea, dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce s-a dezagregat de corpul material. Dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cum spune F.W.H. Myers <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n cartea lui „Personalitatea Uman<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>”, oper<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> care sintetizeaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> o mare parte din lucr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile Societ<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii pentru Cercet<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri Psihice:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Observa<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iile, experien<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ele <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i deduc<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iile, au f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cut pe mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i cercet<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tori, dintre care fac <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i eu parte, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cread<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-o comunicare direct<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> sau telepatic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, nu numai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntre min<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ile oamenilor ce sunt <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pe p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, ci <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntre min<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ile celor de pe p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nr, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i spiritul celor trecu<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n alt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>. O astfel de descoperire, deschide <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ea u<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a unei revela<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Am ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tat c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, printre multe <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>el<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ciuni datorate <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i altora <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i nou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ine, printre multe fraude <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>reri, totu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ajung p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> la noi, adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rate manifest<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri a celor de dincolo de morm<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Prin descoperiri <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i prin revela<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii, s-au statornicit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n mod provizoriu unele teorii, cu privire la sufletele celor disp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ru<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, cu care am izbutit s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> intr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n leg<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Mai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>i de toate, eu, cel pu<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>in, g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sesc pricini de a crede, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> starea lor e o stare de necontenit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tere <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elepciune <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i iubire. Iubirile lor de pe p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n neschimbate, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i mai ales acele iubiri mai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nalte, care se revars<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n adorare <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nchinare... P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>catul li se pare lor, nu at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t un lucru <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ngrozitor, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t o robie. Nu e <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntrupat <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n chipul vreunui puternic Potentat i mai degrab<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> e o nebunie care desparte pe om de semenii s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>i, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de care spiritele desc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ate caut<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntuiasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> sufletul schilodit. Nu e nevoie de pedeapsa focului; a se cunoa<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te pe sine <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i e pedeapsa, precum <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>splata omului; a se cunoa<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te pe sine <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a fia apropiat <text:soft-page-break/>sau r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zle<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>it de sufletele tovar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>ilor. C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n acea lume, iubirea e singura p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toare de via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>; apropiata tov<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>ie cu Sfin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii, nu e numai podoaba vie<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii ve<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>nice, ci alc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tuie<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>i Acea Via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>. Ba mai mult <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>: reiese din legile telepatiei, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> acea tov<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>ie ne folose<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te nou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de pe acum. Chiar de pe acum, amintirea noastr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> duioas<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> - dragostea e <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>i o rug<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ciune - sprijin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>re<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te acele suflete desc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ate, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n drumul lor spre culmi”.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Potrivirea acestor p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>reri, care sunt <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntemeiate pe am<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>nun<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ite cercet<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri psihice, cu <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþã</text:span>turile Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>, e <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r vrednic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de amintit.</text:p>
