    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Sunte<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i rodul aceluia<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pom, frunzele aceleia<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ramuri, florile acelea<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i gr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>dini”. Aceasta e una din spusele cele mai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsemnate ale lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i mai este una asem<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toare: „Nu trebuie sl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>vit cel ce-<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i iube<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ara, ci cel ce iube<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te neamul omenesc”. Unitatea - unitatea lui Dumnezeu, a omenirii <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a tuturor f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>pturilor create - e punctul fundamental, al <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþã</text:span>turii lui. Aici iar se v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>de<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te potrivirea dintre adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rata religie <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tiin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>. Cu fiecare pas f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cut de <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tiin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>, se vade<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te din ce <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ce mai limpede unitatea universului <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i leg<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tura dintre toate p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ile lui. Domeniul astronomului e nedesp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>it de al fizicianului, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i al fizicianului de al chimistului, al chimistului de al biologului, al biologului de al psihologului, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a mai departe. Fiece descoperire nou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n orice c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mp de cercetare, arunc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> lumini noi, asupra altor c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mpuri. Precum au ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tat <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tiin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ele fizice c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> orice atom de materie, din univers, atrage pe to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i ceilal<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i atomi <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i are o <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nr<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>urire asupra lor, oric<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t de mici <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de dep<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rtate ar fie ele, tot astfel, descoper<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> acuma <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tiin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ele psihice, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fiecare suflet, din univers, are o <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nr<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>urire asupra tuturor celorlalte. Prin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ul Kropotkin, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n cartea sa despre <text:span text:style-name="T21">Ajutorul mutual</text:span>, arat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> foarte limpede, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i la animalele cele mai de jos, e neap<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nevoie de ajutorul mutual, pentru men<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>inerea vie<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii, pe c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd printre oameni, prop<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>irea civiliza<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iei at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rn<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nlocuirea treptat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a du<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>niei, prin ajutorul mutual. „Fiecare pentru to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i pentru fiecare”, e singurul principiu pe temeiul c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ruia poate progresa o comunitate.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T22">Era Unit</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">ãþ</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">ii.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Toate semnele vremurilor de azi, ne arat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> am ajuns la zorile unei ere noi, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n istoria omenirii. P<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> acum, t<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ra acvil<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a omenirii, s-a <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>inut str<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ns de vechiul cuib <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n st<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nca neclintit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a egoismului <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a materialismului. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>ncerc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile ei, de a-<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntrebuin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a aripile au fost scurte <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i sfioase. A sim<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>it necontenit o n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zuin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>, spre ceva <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> neatins. Din ce <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ce mai mult s-a sim<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>it st<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>njenit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n str<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nsoarea vechilor <text:soft-page-break/>dogme <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i crezuri. Dar acum, s-a sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it era de <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>are, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i acvila se poate av<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nta pe aripile credin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ei <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ale ra<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iunii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n lumile mai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nalte ale dragostei spirituale <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ale adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rului. Nu va mai fi lipit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt ca p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> acum, aripile i-au crescut <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i se vor <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n voia lor, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n sfera largilor priveli<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a minunatei libert<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>i. Un lucru <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, e de nevoie: ca s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fie zborul ei sigur <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i neprimejduit; - Aripile ei trbuie nu numai s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fie puternice, ci s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se mi<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te cu deplin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> armonie <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i potrivire <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntre ele.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cum spune ‘Abdul-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Nu se poate zbura numai cu o arip<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncearc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> zboare numai cu aripa religiei, va c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>dea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n mla<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tina supersti<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iei, iar dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncearc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> zboare numai cu aripa <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tiin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ei, <text:span text:style-name="T5">îº</text:span>i va sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i zborul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n viroaga <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntunecoas<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a materialismului”. - Cuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri la Paris, p.132.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Armonia des<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>v<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntre religie <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tiin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>, este condi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ia sine qua non, a unei vie<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i mai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nalte a omenirii. C<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd se va ajunge la aceasta, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd fiecare copil va fi crescut nu numai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tiin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elor <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i al artelor, dat tot at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n iubire pentru <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntreaga omenire <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n radioasa supunere la Voin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a lui Dumnezeu, a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a cum ni se dezv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>luie <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n progresul evolu<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iei, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþã</text:span>mintele profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ilor, atunci <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i numai atunci, va veni <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ia Domnului <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i va fi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mplinit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Voin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a Lui, precum <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ceruri a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pe p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt; atunci <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i numai atunci, Pacea Cea Mare <text:span text:style-name="T5">îº</text:span>i va rev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rsa binecuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile peste lumea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntreag<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„C<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd religia”, zice ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, „dezb<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de supersti<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii, tradi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i dogme neluminate, <text:span text:style-name="T5">îº</text:span>i va ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ta conformitatea cu <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tiin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a, atunci va fi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n lume o mare putere purificatoare, aduc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toare de unitate, care va izgoni orice r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zboire, vrajb<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, ne<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elegere <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i lupt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i atunci va fi omenirea unit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n puterea iubirii de Dumnezeu”. - Cuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri la Paris, p.135.</text:p>
