    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T22">Interpretarea profe</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">þ</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">iilor.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:soft-page-break/>Se <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tie c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t e de grea, interpretarea profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iilor <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu e subiect asupra c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ruia s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se deosebeasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> mai mult, p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rerile <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>a<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ilor. Aceasta n-are de ce s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ne mire, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci, dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cum spun chiar scripturile revelate, multe din profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii au fost date sub o astfel de form<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t nu puteau fi deslu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elese, p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeplineau, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i chiar <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i atunci, numai de cei ce erau cura<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i la suflet <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i desc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i de prejudec<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>i. Astfel la sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>itul vedeniilor lui Daniel, iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce a fost spus profetului:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Iar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> tu, Daniel, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nchide-<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i cuvintele <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pecetluie<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te-<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i cartea, p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> la ceasul sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>itului; mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i vor alerga de colo p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> colo <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cunoa<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>terea se va m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri... <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i auzit-am, dar n-am priceput; atunci zis-am: „O, Dumnezeul meu, care va fi sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>itul acestor lucruri?” <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i El a zis: „Umbl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n calea ta Daniel, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> vorbele sunt <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nchise <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cartea pecetluit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> la sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>itul vremurilor.” - Daniel XII 4-10.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Dumnezeu, a pecetluit profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iile p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> la timpul cuvenit <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i n-a dezv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>luit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elesul lor deplin nici m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>car profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ilor care le-au rostit, ne putem <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncredin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nimeni dec<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t Solul ales de Dumnezeu va fi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n stare s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> rup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pecetea <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> dea la lumin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elesul cuprins <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n chivotul parabolelor profetice. C<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd cuget<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m asupra istoriei profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ilor <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i asupra interpret<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii lor gre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ite <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n veacurile <text:span text:style-name="T5">ºî</text:span> vremurile trecute, precum <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i asupra<text:span text:style-name="T21"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">î</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">ndrum</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">rilor</text:span> solemne date de profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i, e firesc s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> sim<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>im nevoia de marea chibzuire, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nainte de a primi deslu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>irile propuse de teologi privitor la adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ratul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>eles al acestor rostiri <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i la modul cum au fost <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeplinite. Pe de alt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> parte, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd se ive<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te cineva care-<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rturise<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te misiunea de a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeplini profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iile, e de neap<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nevoie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-i cercet<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m menirea cu mintea liber<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ne<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntunecat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de prejudec<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>i.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">De s-ar <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mpla s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fie un impostor, frauda va fi u<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>or descoperit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i nici o urmare rea nu se va ivi, vai celor ce cu nep<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sare gonesc de la u<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a lor pe Trimisul lui Dumnezeu, pentru c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a venit neprevestit, sub o <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nf<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>i<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>are nea<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>teptat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþã</text:span>mintele lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, dovedesc c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> e Cel F<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n toate c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ile Sfinte, care are puterea s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> rup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pece<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ile profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ilor, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> toarne tuturor „nepre<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>uitul vin pecetluit”, al misterelor divine. Ne gr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>bim, a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>adar, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> auzim l<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>muririle lui <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cercet<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n lumina lor, cuvintele cunoscute, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> adesea misterioase, rostite de profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii de demult.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P20">Venirea Domnului.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Venirea Domnului, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n zilele din urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>” este singura „dep<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rtat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mplare divin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>” pe care o a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>teapt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pe care c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n cele mai minunate c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri ale lor. S<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> vedem, acum ce <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsemneaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> „Venirea Domnului?” De bun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> seam<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, Dumnezeu <text:s/>e totdeauna l<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ng<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>pturile Lui, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n toate cele <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i peste toate; „Ne e mai aproape dec<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t suflarea noastr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, mai lipit de noi, dec<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>inile <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i picioarele <text:soft-page-break/>noastre.” Da, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> omul nu poate vedea nici auzi pe Dumnezeu imanent <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i transcendent, nu-<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i poate da seama de prezen<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a Lui, p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu se dezv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>luie ochilor lui sub o form<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> vizibil<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu voebe<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te cu el <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n graiul omenesc. Dumnezeu totdeauna s-a slujit de o unealt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> uman<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, pentru a-<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i revela cele mai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nalte atribute. Fiecare profet a fost un mijlocitor, prin care Dumnezeu s-a cobor<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t printre poporul s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:s/>i-a gr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>it. Isus a fost unul din aceti mijlocitori, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tinii cu drept cuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, au socotit ivirea Lui, ca venirea Domnului. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>ntr-<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsul ei v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Chipul lui Dumnezeu <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i prin buzele Lui, auzir<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Glasul lui Dumnezeu. Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h ne spune c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> „Venirea” Dumnezeului O<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tirilor, Tat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l Etern, F<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>torul lumii <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i M<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntuitorul ei, care dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> spusele tuturor profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ilor, se va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mpla la „sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>itul tuturor vremurilor,” nu <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsemneaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nimic alt, dec<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tarea Lui, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr- <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntruchipare omeneasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, precum s-a ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tat <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n templul trupesc al lui Iisus din Nazaret, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de data asta, cu o revela<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ie mai plin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i mai str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lucit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, pentru care Iisus <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii dinaintea lui, au venit s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> preg<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>teasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> inimile <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i min<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ile oamenilor.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T22">Profe</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">þ</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">iile privitoare la Iisus.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Din pricin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> n-au fost <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elese profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iile privitoare la timpul venirii Mesiei, Evreii au respins pe Iisus.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce spune ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Evreii a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>teapt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, sosirea Mesiei <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i se roag<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> lui Dumnezeu zi <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i noapte, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-i gr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>beasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> venirea. C<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd a venit Iisus, L-au acuzat <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i L-au ucis zic<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd: Acesta nu e Cel a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>teptat. Iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd va veni Mesia, semne <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i minuni vor m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rturisi c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> e <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r Christul.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Mesia se va ridica dintr-un ora<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span> necunoscut. Se va a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>eza pe tronul lui David, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, va veni cu sabie de o<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>el <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i va c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rmui ca un sceptru de fier. El va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mplini Legea profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ilor. Va cuceri r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ritul <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Apusul <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i va pream<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri pe poporul S<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u ales, Evreii. Va aduce cu El domnia P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n care p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i fiarele vor <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceta de a se mai du<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ni cu omul. C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci, iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, lupul i mielul vor ad<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>pa la acela<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>u, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i toate f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>pturile Domnului, vor vie<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ui <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n lini<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te... Astfel g<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndeau <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i vorbeau Evreii, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci nu <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elegeau Scriptele, nici minunatele adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ruri, cuprinse <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ele. Litera lor, o <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tiau pe de rost, dar din Spiritul lor d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tor de lumin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, nu pricepeau nici un cuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt. </text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Ascult<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> voi ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ta eu, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elesul lor: cu toate c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Hristos a venit din Nazaret, care era un loc cunoscut, venea din Ceruri. Trupu Lui s-a n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>scut din Maria, dar Duhul Lui, venea din Ceruri. Sabia pe care o purta, era sabia graiului, cu care a <text:soft-page-break/>desp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>it binele de r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u, adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rul de minciun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, credinciosul de necredincios <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i lumina de <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntuneric. Vorba Lui, era <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r, o vorb<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ioas<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>! Tronul pe care s-a a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ezat e Tronul Etern, de pe care Hristos domne<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te pentru vecie, un tron ceresc, nu unul p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntesc, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci lucrurile p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nte<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti sunt trec<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toare, iar cele cere<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti nu trec. El t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i des<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>v<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Legea lui Moise <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mplini pe a Profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ilor. Cuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul Lui, cuceri R<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ritul <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Apusul. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ia lui e Ve<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>nic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. El a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>at pe acei Evrei, care L-au recunoscut. Erau oameni <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i femei de teap<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> smerit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> dar al<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>turarea cu Isus <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>i f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cu mari, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i le d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>du <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>are nepieritoare.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Animalele care aveau s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> tr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>iasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n pace unele cu altele, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nseamn<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> diferitele secte <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i rase, care p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> atunci <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zboi, aveau <text:span text:style-name="T5">ºã</text:span> tr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>iasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de acum laolalt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, cu dragoste <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i mil<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, b<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpreun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Apa Vie<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii, din Eternul Izvor al lui Iisus.” - Cuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri la Paris, p. 48.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cea mai mare parte din cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tini, primesc aceste interpret<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri a profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iilor Mesianice, ca fiind privitoare la Iisus, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span> tde spre profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iile asem<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toare, privitoare la Mesia din zilele noastre, mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i cretini le <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mpin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cum au f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cut Evreii <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>teapt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> vreo <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mplare minunat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n planul material, care s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mplineasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n toate am<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>nuntele, litera profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iilor.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T22">Profe</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">þ</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">iile privitoare la B</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">á</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">b </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">º</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">i Bah</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">á</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">’u’ll</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">á</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">h.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> interpretarea Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>, profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iile care vorbesc despre „sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>itul veacurilor”, „ziua cea din urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>”, despre venirea „Dumnezeului O<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tirilor”, a „Tat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lui Etern”, se refer<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeosebi, nu la venirea lui Iisus Hristos, ci la a lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">S<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> lu<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m bun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>oar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, binecunoscuta profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ie a lui Isaia:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Poporul care umbla <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntuneric, a v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zut o mare lumin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, cei care erau <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ara umbrelor mor<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii, asupra lor a str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lucit lumina... C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci tu ai f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mat jugul poverii lui <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i toiagul um<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rului lui, varga de fier a asupritorului lui, ca <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n zilele Midianului. C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci fiecare lupt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a viteazului, e cu zgomot <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>eal<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cu haine muiate <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n s<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nge, dar aceasta, va fi cu p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rjol <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i j<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ratec. C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci ni s-a n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>scut nou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> un prunc <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i un fiu ne-a fost dat <text:span text:style-name="T5">ºî</text:span> c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rmuirea va fi pe umerii lui <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i numele lui va fi Minunatul, Sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tuitorul, Puternicul Dumnezeu, Tat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l Etern, Prin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ul P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cii. Nu va avea sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rirea c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rmuirii Lui <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i o pace f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it va da scaunului de domnie a lui David <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>iei lui, o va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i o va sprijini prin judecat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i neprih<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>nire, de acum <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i-n veci de veci, iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce va face r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>vna Domnului o<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tirilor.” - Isaia IX. 2-7.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Aceasta e una din profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iile, care au fost adesea privite ca referitoare la Hristos, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i o mare parte dintr-<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsa, se poate cu dreptate t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci astfel, dar cu pu<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>in<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cercetare va ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ta; cu c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t mai bine <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i mai deplin, se potrive<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te cu Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Hristos, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r a fost un aduc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tor de lumin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i un M<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntuitor, dar timp de <text:soft-page-break/>aproape dou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> mii de ani, dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> venirea Lui, marea majoritate a popoarelor de pe p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i-au urmat drumul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntuneric, iar copiii lui Israel <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i al<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i copii ai lui Dumnezeu, n-au <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncetat de a geme, sub varga asupritorilor. Pe de alt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> parte, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n timpul primelor decade ale erei Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>, lumina adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rului str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lucise asupra R<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ritului <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Apusului <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a fost purtat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n toate <text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>rile de pe p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, evanghelia care ne arat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pe Dumnezeu ca tat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pe oameni ca fra<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, marile autocra<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii militare au fost risipite <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i s-a n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>scut o Lig<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a Na<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iunilor, care ne aduce n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>dejdea unei grabnice m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntuiri pentru na<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ionalit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ile strivite <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i asuprite <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n lumea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntreag<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Marele r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zboi, care de cur<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd a zguduit lumea, cu nemaipomenita sa <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntrebuin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>are de arme de foc, foc lichid, bombe incendiare <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i focul mainilor, a fost <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r cu „p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rjol <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i j<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ratec”. Bah’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, care -sa <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeletnicit pe l<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ng<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> scrierile sale, cu probleme privitoare la c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rmuire <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i administra<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ie <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tat cum ar putea fi mai bine dezlegate, a luat „c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rmuirea pe umerii lui”, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-un chip cum n-a f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cut-o niciodat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Hristos. C<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t despre titluri de „Tat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l Etern”, „Prin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span> al P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cii”, bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, adesea vorbe<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te de el <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ca de Fiul omului, iar Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h declar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> menirea lui, e de a aduce pacea pe p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, pe c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd Hristos a zis: „Nu am venit s-aduc pacea ci sabia”, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de fapt, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n tot timpul erei cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tine, s-au <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>inut <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ir r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zboaiele <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i luptele <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntre secte.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P20">Slava lui Dumnezeu.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Numele „Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h”, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nseamn<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n limba arab<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> „Slava lui Dumnezeu” <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i acest nume aidoma e adesea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntrebuin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>at de profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii evrei, pentru Cel F<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duit, ce va s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se arate <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n zilele cele de pe urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. De pild<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n capitolul al 40-lea din Isaia citim:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">M<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ng<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ie-te o poporul meu, zice Domnul. Vorbe<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n lini<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te Ierusalimului <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i spune-i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a luat sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zboiul lui <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> e iertat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nelegiuirea lui, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci primise de la Domnul m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndoit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pentru p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>catele lui. Glasul celui care striga <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n pustiu, preg<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ti<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile Domnului, croi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n pustiu o c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rare dreapt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntru M<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rirea Domnului. Fiecare vale va fi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>at<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i fiecare munte <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i deal va fi <text:span text:style-name="T21">mic</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">º</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">orat</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i tot ce e str<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mb va fi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndreptat <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i tot ce e aspru se va netezi: <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T21">Slava Domnului</text:span> se va ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ta tuturor, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i toat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ptura laolalt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> o va vedea.”</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ia de mai sus, aceasta a fost <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n mare parte <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeplinit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> prin venirea lui Hristos <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a premerg<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>torului Lui Ioan Botez<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>torul, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> numai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n parte, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n zilele lui Hristos, r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zboiul Ierusalimul nu luase sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it; multe veacuri de <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncerc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i umiliri, erau preg<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tite pentru el.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:soft-page-break/>Cu sosirea lui B<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>b <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a lui B<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>h<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncepe s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se arate, o mai des<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>v<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mplinire, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci chiar de pe acuma, au r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rit zori mai luminoase pentru Ierusalim <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>dejdea lui <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-un viitor pa<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>nic <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ucit pare acum temeinic <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndrept<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>it<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Alte profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii vorbesc despre M<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntuitorul Israelului, Slava lui Dumnezeu, care va s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> vie <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, din locul r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ritului soarelui. Or, Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, s-a ivit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Persia, care e la Est de Ierusalim, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nspre soare r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sare <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a venit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul Sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, unde a petrecut ultimii dou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zeci de ani ai vie<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii lui. Dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ar fi venit acolo de bun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> voie, lumea ar fi putut crede c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> e o viclenie a unui impostor, pentru a se conforma profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iilor, dar el a venit ca surghiunit <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i prizonier, a fost trimis acolo de <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>ahul Persiei <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de Sultanul Turciei. Cu greu <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>i putem b<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>nui c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ar fi c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>utat s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> aduc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> dovezi de temeinicia declara<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iei lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n care se d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>dea drept „Slava lui Dumnezeu”, a c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rei venire fusese vestit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P20">Ziua domnului.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul „Zi” <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n fraze ca „ziua Domnului” sau „Ziua cea de pe urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>”, trebuie interpretat ca <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsemn<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd „Epoc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>”. Fiecare mare <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntemeietor de religie, are „Ziua” lui. Fiecare e ca un soare. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþã</text:span>turile lui au zorile lor, apoi adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rul lor lumineaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> din ce <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ce mai mult inimile <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i min<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ile popoarelor, p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ating zenitul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nr<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>uririi lor. Apoi treptat se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntunec<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, se interpreteaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> gre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it, se r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>st<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ce<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i umbra <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>luie p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sare soarele unei zile noi. Ziua Manifest<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii Supreme a lui Dumnezeu, este ziua cea de pe urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci e o zi, care nu se va sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i niciodat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i nu va fi biruit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de noapte. Soarele ei nu va pune niciodat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i nu va fi biruit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de noapte. Soarele ei nu va apune niciodat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, ci va lumina sufletele oamenilor <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i-n lumea aceasta <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i-n cealalt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">La drept vorbind, nici un soare spiritual nu apune vreodat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Soarele lui Moise, al lui Hristos, al lui Mahomed <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i al altor profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>luce<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pe Cer, cu o lumin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ne<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tirbit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>ns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> norii ridica<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i de pe p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, i-au ascuns str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lucirea, de ochii neamului omenesc. Soarele Suprem al lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, va risipi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-o zi, acei nori <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntuneco<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i, astfel <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t popoarele tuturor religiilor, se vor bucura <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n lumina tuturor profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ilor <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i toate laolalt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> vor sl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>vi pe acela<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Dumnezeu, a c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rui lumin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> au oglindit-o to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T22">Profe</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">þ</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">ii privitoare la ‘Abdu’l-Bah</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">á</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iile lui Isaia, ale lui Ieremia, ale lui Ezechiel <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ale lui Zaharia, se pomene<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n mai multe r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nduri despre un om pe care ei <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>l numesc Ramura. Acest nume adeseori, a fost privit de cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tini, ca referitor la Hristos, dar Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>i socotesc <text:soft-page-break/>c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se refer<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeosebi <text:s/>la ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>. Datina e <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Persia, de a pomeni de fiul cel mai mare al unei familii, sub numele de „Ramura cea mare”, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, ca un fiu mai mare al lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, e de obicei cunoscut de Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>, sub acest nume. Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n scrierile sale, adesea vorbe<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te de el <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ca de Pomul, sau de R<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cina, iar de ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, ca de Ramur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, el <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i scrie, cum urmeaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„’Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span> e Miezul Legei lui Dumnezeu, e Ramura care r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sare din Pom. Partea de c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>petenie e Pomul, temelia e Pomul <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rul universal e Pomul.” - Steaua Apusului, vol.VIII nr. 17, pg.325.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cea mai lung<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ie Biblic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, referitoare la Ramura, se g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>se<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n capitolul 11-lea din Isaia:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„<text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i atunci va ie<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i un l<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>star din tulpina lui Jese <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i o ramur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> va cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te din r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cinile ei: <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i se va opri asupra lui Duhul lui Dumnezeu, duhul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elepciunii <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i al p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>trunderii, duhul sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tuirii <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i al puterii, <text:s/>duhul cunoa<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>terii <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i al temerii de Dumnezeu... dreptatea va fi br<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ul <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>alelor lui <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i credincio<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ia br<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ul mijlocului lui. <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i va locui atunci, lupul al<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>turi de miel, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pardosul al<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>turi de ciut<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i vi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elul <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i puiul de leu <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ieduk laolalt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i un copila<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>i va m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>na... Nu vor v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ta <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i nu vor d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ma nimic <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n muntele meu sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul va fi plin de cunoa<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>terea lui Dumnezeu, a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a cum apa acoper<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile.. <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i aceasta se va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mpla <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ziua c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd Domnul <text:span text:style-name="T5">îº</text:span>i va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntinde m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>na a doua oar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, ca s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>scumpere r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>i<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a poporului S<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u, risipit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Asiria <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Egipt, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Patros<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Etiopia, la Elam, la <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>incar <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i la Hamat <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ostroavele m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii. El va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a un steag pentru neamuri, va str<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nge pe surghiuni<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii lui Israel <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i va aduna pe cei risipi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i ai lui Iuda, de la cele patru col<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>uri ale p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntului.” - Isaia XI 1-13.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, spune urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toarele asupra unei alte profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii, referitoare la Ramur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Una din marile <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mpl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri ce se vor ivi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ziua manifest<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii a acelei Ramuri f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> seam<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>n, e <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>area stindardului lui Dumnezeu printre toate neamurile, adic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> toate neamurile <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i triburile <text:s/>se vor aduna la umbra acestei divine Flamuri, care nu e alt, dec<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>i m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rea<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a Ramur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i toate se vor face un singur neam. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>nver<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>unarea credin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elor <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a religiilor, una <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpotriva altora, du<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>nia dintre rase <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i popoare <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i deosebirile de patrie, vor fi plivite dintre ele. Toate vor ajunge o singur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> religie, o singur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> credin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>, o singur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ra<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i un singur popor, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i vor tr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-o singur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de ba<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, care e globul p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntesc. Se va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntemeia <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntre toate neamurile pacea universal<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i buna <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nvoire. Ramura f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> seam<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>n va aduna laolalt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pe tot Israel, - adic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n acest ciclu tot poporul evreu care e risipit Apus <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i R<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rit, la miaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-noapte <text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i la miaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-zi, va fi adunat la un loc <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul Sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Acum vede<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i: aceste <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mpl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri nu s-au ivit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ciclul cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tin, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci neamurile nu s-au adunat toate sub un singur stindard, care e divina Ramur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Dar <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n acest ciclu al Dumnezeului O<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tirilor, toate neamurile <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i popoarele vor intra sub umbra acestei flamuri.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">De asemenea, nici Israel, risipit pe toat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fa<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntului, n-a fost adunat laolalt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul Sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n timpul ciclului cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tin, dar la <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceputul ciclului lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> divin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a cum e limpede rostit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n toate c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ile profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ilor, a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceput s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se adevereasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Pute<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i vedea c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> din toate p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ile lumii, se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndreapt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> spre P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul Sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, triburi de evrei; tr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>iesc <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n sate <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mpii, pe care le st<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nesc <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i zi cu zi se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nmul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>esc <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t toat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Palestina, va ajunge <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ara lor.” - R<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>spunsuri la c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>teva <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntreb<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri, p.75</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">De c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd au fost scrise cele de mai sus, Palestina a trecut din m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>inile turcilor <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i „Puterii Aliate”, au <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncurajat <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntemeierea unei patrii na<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ionale a evreilor <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Palestina.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">De la r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zboiul cel mare, am v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zut <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntemeierea unei Ligi a Na<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iunilor precum <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i un congres interna<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ional cu scopul de a stabili o reducere simultan<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a armamentelor. Acestea arat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> s-a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>naintat cu un mare pas spre <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeplinirea unei <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsemnate p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i din profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iile privitoare la pacea interna<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ional<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P20"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T22">Ziua judec</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">ãþ</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">ii.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Hristos a vorbit mult <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n parabole despre marea Zi a judec<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd „Fiul Omului va veni <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n slava Tat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lui s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i va r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>spl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ti pe fiecare om, dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> faptele lui” (Matei XVI 27). El asemuie<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te acea Zi, cu ziua seceri<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ului, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd se arde neghina iar gr<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ul e adunat <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n hambare:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„A<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a va fi la sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>itul vremurilor (la <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mplinirea veacurilor). Fiul omului <text:span text:style-name="T5">îº</text:span>i va trimite <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ngerii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ei vor aduna din <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ia Lui, toate lucrurile ce vat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">ºî</text:span> pe to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i cei ce fac nelegiuiri, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>i va arunca <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-un cuptor de foc: atunci vor fi gemete <text:span text:style-name="T5">ºî</text:span> scr<text:span text:style-name="T5">âº</text:span>nirea din<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ilor. Atunci vor str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>luci cei drep<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, ca soarele <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ia Tat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lui lor.” - Matei XII 40-43.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul „sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>itul lumii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntrebuin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>at <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n versiunea autorizat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a Bibliei, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n acest pasaj <text:span text:style-name="T5">ºî</text:span> altele asem<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toare, a f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cut pe mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nchipuie c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ziua judec<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii de apoi, p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul va fi deodat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nimicit, dar aceasta e de bun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> seam<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> o gre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>eal<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ratul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>eles al frazei pare a fi „<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mplinirea sau sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>irea veacurilor.” Hristos ne <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nva<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ia Tat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lui, se va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntemeia pe p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, precum <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Ceruri. Ne <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nva<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ne rug<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m: „Vie <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ia Ta: Precum <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Cer a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pe p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt.”</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n parabola cu via, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd Tat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l, st<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nul viei, vine s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pedepseasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pe arenda<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>, nu <text:soft-page-break/>nimice<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te via (lumea) ci o <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nchiriaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> altor arenda<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i, care <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>i vor da roadele la vremea lor.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul nu are s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fie nimicit, ci va fi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nnoit <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ren<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>scut. Hristos, cu alt prilej vorbe<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te de acea zi, ca re<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nnoirea, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd Fiul Omului, vor sta pe tronul Slavei lui.” Sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul Petru vorbe<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te de ea, ca de „vremea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mprosp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii” „vremea prefacerii tuturor Sfin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ilor lui Profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, de la <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceputul lumii.” Ziua judec<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii despre care vorbe<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te Iisus Hristos, e desigur acela<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cu ziua c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd va veni Dumnezeul O<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tirilor, Tat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l, care a fost proorocit de Isaia <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii din Vechiul Testament, va fi timpul marilor pedepse pentru cei r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>i, dar va fi un timp <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n care se va statornici dreptatea <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i va domni pe p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt ca <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ceruri. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n interpretarea Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>, venirea fiec<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rei Manifest<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri a lui Dumnezeu e o zi de judecat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, dar venirea supremei Manifest<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri, Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, e ziua cea mare a judec<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii, pentru ciclul p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntesc <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n care tr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>im. Chemarea <text:span text:style-name="T21">buciumului </text:span>de care au voebit Hristos, Mahomed <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i al<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, e chemarea Manifest<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii, care sun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pentru to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i cei de pe p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i din ceruri - cei <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntrupa<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cei ce <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i-au p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sit trupul. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>lnirea lui Dumnezeu, prin Manifestarea Lui, e pentru cei ce doresc s