    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþã</text:span>mintele Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>nvierea n-are nimic de a face cu trupul material <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i solid. Acel trup, odat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce a murit, e sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it. Se descompune, iar atomii lui, niciodat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu se vor mai aduna spre a alc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tui acela<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i trup. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>nvierea e na<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>terea individului la via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a spiritual<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, prin harul Duhului Sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ruit de manifestarea lui Dumnezeu. Morm<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul din care se ridic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, e morm<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul necunoa<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>terii <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a nep<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii, fa<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> de Dumnezeu. Somnul din care se de<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>teapt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, e starea de adormire spiritual<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n care mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>teapt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> zorile Zilei lui Dumnezeu. Aceste zori lumineaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, pe to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i cei ce au tr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>it pe fa<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntului, fie c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> sunt <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntrupa<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, fie c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i-au p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sit trupul, dar cei ce sunt orbi spiritualice<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te, nu le pot z<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri. Ziua <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>nvierii nu e o zi de dou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zeci <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i patru de ore, ci o er<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> care a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceput de pe acum <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i va d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>inui c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t ciclul lumesc din care facem parte. Luceaf<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rul dimine<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii acelei zile este B<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>b, soarele ei, e suprema Manifestare a lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i luna ei, e ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span> - o stea, un soare, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i o lun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, care nu vor apune niciodat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i nu vor <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceta de a str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>luci <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n lumea spiritual<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd se vor fi <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ters de pe fa<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntului orice urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a civiliza<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iei.</text:p>
