    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n multe din convorbirile Sale, Hristos vorbe<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te despre viitoarea Manifestare a lui <text:soft-page-break/>Dumnezeu, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n persoana a treia, iar <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n altele, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntrebuin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>eaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> persoana <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ia. Iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce spune: „M<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> duc s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> preg<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tesc un loc. <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> duc s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> preg<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tesc locul, am s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> viu <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nd<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>t <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i am s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> primesc la mine.” (Ioan XIV 2). <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n primul capitol, al Faptelor Apostolilor, citim c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> s-a spus ucenicilor, la <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>area lui Iisus: „Acela<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Iisus, care se ridic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de la voi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n cer, va veni tot a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a, cum l-a<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zut ridic<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndu-se la cer. „Din pricina acestor spuse <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a altora asem<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toare, mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tini a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>teapt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> atunci c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd va veni Fiul Omului, pe „norii cerului <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cu mare slav<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>”, vor vedea cu chip trupesc pe acela<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Iisus, care umbla pe str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zile Ierusalimului acum dou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> mii de ani <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i care a s<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ngerat <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>timit pe cruce. Ei a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>teapt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i poat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> v<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span> degetele <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n semnele de pe picioarele <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de pe m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>inile Lui <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>na, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n rana lancei, din coasta lui. Dar desigur o cugetare c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>tu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de pu<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>in ad<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ncit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> asupra cuvintelor rostite de Iisus, ar risipi o asemenea p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rere. Evreii din timpul lui Iisus, aveau <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntocmai acelea<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i idei, asupra <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntoarcerii lui Ilie, dar iisus le-a l<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>murit gre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>eala lor <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i le-a ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tat c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ia cum c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> „Ilie trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> vie mai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>i”, a fost <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mplinit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, nu prin <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntoarcerea f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>pturii trupe<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti a fostului Ilie, ci <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n persoana lui Ioan Botez<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>torul, care a venit „<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n duhul <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i puterea lui Ilie.” „Iar dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> vre<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-l primi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i” a spus Iisus, „acesta e Ilie, care