, a fost <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeplinit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, prin ivirea lui B<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>b <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i prin venirea lui proprie.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce spune:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> soarele de ast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zi ar zice, Eu sunt soarele de ieri! E adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat, de asemeni, dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> potrivit scurgerii zilelor ar zice, Eu sunt altul dec<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t soarele de ieri, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> e adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat. De asemeneni, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> privim zilele; dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> s-ar spune c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> toate zilele sunt acelea<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i, e <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndrept<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>it <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> s-ar spune, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> socotind zilele <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i menirea lor, se deosebesc unele de altele <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i aceasta e adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat, dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cum vezi. C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci, cu toate c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> sunt acelea<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i, totu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n fiecare e un nume, o <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ire <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i o menire, care o deosebesc de celelalte. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n acela<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i chip <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cu aceea<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i interpretare, trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elege<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i st<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile de deosebire, diferen<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ele <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i identitatea Sfintelor Manifest<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri, ca s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i dai seama de <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elesul Cuvintelor Creatorului Numelor <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Atributelor, privitoare la deosebire <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i unitate.” - Cartea Iq<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>n, p.15.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:soft-page-break/>Iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce spune ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Afla<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> venirea lui Hristos a doua oar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>,k nu <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nseamn<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ceea ce crede poporul, ci mai degrab<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nseamn<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ivirea Celui al c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rui venire a fost f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> D<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nsul. Va veni cu <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ia Domnului <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cu Puterea Lui, care a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nconjurat p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul. Aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> st<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nire va fi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n lumea inimilor <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a spiritelor, iar nu <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n lumea materiei, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci lumea material<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, nu se poate asemui, nici cu o aip<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de musc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ochii lui Dumnezeu, dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ar fi dintre acei ce <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tiu! Cu adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat, Hristos a venit cu <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ia Lui, chiar de la <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceputul care n-a avut <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceput, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i va veni cu mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ia Lui a vecilor tuturor vecilor, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntruc<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n acest <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>eles, Hristos, e o manifestare a Realit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii Divine, Esen<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a curat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cereasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, Substan<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> care n-are nici <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceput nici sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it, Are o <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nf<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>i<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>are, r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sare <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i apune ca manifestare <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n fiecare ciclu.” - Scrisorile lui ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, vol. I, p.138.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T22">Timpul Sf</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">â</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">r</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">º</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">itului</text:span>.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Hristos <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Apostolii Lui, au pomenit de multe semne prin care avea s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se deosebeasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> timpul „<text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>ntoarcerii”, Fiul Omului, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n slava Tat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lui. Iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce a spus Hristos:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Iar c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd ve<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i vedea Ierusalimul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nconjurat de o<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tiri, atunci s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pieirea lui e aproape... C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci acelea vor fi zilele r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zbun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii, ca s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mplineasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> toate cele scrise... c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci va fi mare pr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>d <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nie asupra acestui popor. <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i vor c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>dea de t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>i<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ul sabiei, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i vor fi du<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i robi, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n toate neamurile; iar Ierusalimul va fi c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lcat <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n picioare de neamuri p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mplini vremea Neamurilor”. - Luca XXI 20-24.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>ntr-alt loc spune:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Lua<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i seama s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ele nimeni. C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i vor veni <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n numele Meu, zic<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd „Eu sunt Hristos”; <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i vor <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ela pe oameni. <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i ve<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i auzi de r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zboaie <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de zgomot de r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zboaie: dar s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> tulbura<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i: c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci toate aceste lucruri trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mple, dar sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>itul, n-a venit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci un neam se va ridica <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpotriva altui neam, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ie, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpotriva altei <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii: <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i vor fi foamete <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i molime, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cutremuri <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n diferite locuri. Toate acestea, sunt <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceputul durerilor. <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i atunci v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> vor preda ca s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i asupri<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> vor ucide; <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ve<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i fi ur<text:span text:style-name="T5">âþ</text:span>i de neamurile toate, din pricina numelui Meu. <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i atunci, mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i vor fi v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ma<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i se vor tr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>da unii pe al<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i se vor ur<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span> unii pe al<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii. <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i se vor ridica mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i mincino<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i vor <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ela pe mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pentru c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nmul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i nelegiuirea, se va r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci iubirea multora. Dar cel ce va r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>bda p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> la sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it, acela va fi m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntuit.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T21">Iar aceast</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21"> evanghelie a </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">î</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">mp</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">r</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">ãþ</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">iei, va fi propov</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">duit</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">î</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">n lumea </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">î</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">ntreag</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">, ca o m</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">rturie, pentru toate neamurile; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">º</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">i atunci va veni sf</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">â</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">r</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">º</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">itul”. - Matei XXIV 4-14.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n aceste versete, Hristos a prevestit limpede, f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncojur sau v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l, lucrurile ce <text:soft-page-break/>trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mple <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nainte de venirea Fiului Omului. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n timpul veacurilor ce s-au scurs, de c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd a vorbit Iisus, fiecare din aceste semne, au fost <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mplinite. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T21"> </text:span>partea din urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a fiec<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rui fragment, Iisus pomene<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te de o <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mplare, care va fi semnul c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a venit vremea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntoarcerii Lui - <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-unul din ele, sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>itul exilului evreilor <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i restaurarea Ierusalimului, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n cell<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lalt, porpov<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duirea evangheliei, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n lumea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntreag<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. E uimitor de a vedea, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> am<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> aceste semne, se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeplinesc liter<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cu liter<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, sub ochii no<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tri.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> aceste p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i ale profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iilor sunt tot at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t de adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rate ca <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i celelalte, urmeaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> tr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>im acum <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n „timpul <text:s/>sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>itului”, despre care a vorbit Hristos.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Mahomed <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i el pomene<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te de unele semne care vor d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>inui <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Ziua <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>nvierii. Citim <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Qur’<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>n, urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>torele:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„C<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd a zis All<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h: „O,Iisus! Cu adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat eu te voi face s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> mori, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i te voi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a spre mine, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i te voi cur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>i de <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nvinuirile celor ce nu au credin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i voi pune pe cei ce cred <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n tine (adic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pe cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tini) deasupra celor care nu cred (evrei <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i al<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii) p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Ziua <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>nvierii; atunci la mine te vei <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntoarce, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i atunci eu voi hot<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntre voi, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n privin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a celor <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n care v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> deosebi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i.“. - Surat III 54.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„M<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>na lui Dumnezeu”, au spus evreii „e <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>uit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>”. M<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>inile lor vor fi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>uite, - <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pentru ceea ce au spus, vor fi blestema<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i. Ba mai mult <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>! Am<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>inile Lui sunt <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntinse! <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> voie, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mparte El, darurile. Ceea ce s-a trimis de la Domnul t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u, va m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri desigur r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zvr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tirea <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i necredincio<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ia multor dintre ei; <text:span text:style-name="T5">ºî</text:span> am pus <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntre d<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ii ur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i du<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>nie, care vor d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>inui p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> la cea din urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Zi a <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>nvierii. Adesea, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd vor aprinde ei o lumin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de straj<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pentru r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zboi, Dumnezeu o va stinge”. - Surat V 69.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Iar noi ne-am <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nvoit cu legea celor care zic „suntem cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tini”. Dar ei au uitat o parte din cele <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ate; de aceea am st<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rnit printre ei vr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>jm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>ie <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, care va d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>inui p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Ziua <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>nvierii; iar la sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it le va gr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>i Dumnezeu, despre faptele lor”. - Surat V 18.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Aceste cuvinte <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i au fost liter<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cu liter<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeplinite prin subjugarea evreilor de c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tre cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tini <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i musulmani, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i prin sectele <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ne<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elegerile care au dezbinat <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pe evrei <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pe cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tini, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n toate veacurile de c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd a spus Mahomed acestea. Numai de la <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceputul erei Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>, (Ziua <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>nvierii) s-au ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tat semnele unui apropiat sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it, al acestei st<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri de lucruri.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T22">Semne </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">î</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">n Cer </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">º</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">i pe P</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">m</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">â</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">nt.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ile Sfinte Evreie<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti, Cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tine, Mahomedane <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i multe altele, e o minunat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> asem<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>nare <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n descrierea semnelor care vor <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nso<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i venirea Celui F<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duit.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Citim <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Cartea lui Ioil:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„<text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i voi ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ta minuni <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n cer <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pe p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nge <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i fos, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i st<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>lpi de fum. Soarele se va preface <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntuneric, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i luna <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n s<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nge, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nainte de marea <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ngrozitoarea zi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n care va veni Domnul. C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci, iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n zilele acelea, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd voi aduce iar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>i robia lui Iuda <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a Ierusalimului, voi aduna toate neamurile, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i le voi duce <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n valea Iosafatului, (Iehova a judecat) <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i voi judeca acolo cu d<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ii,... mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>imi peste mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>imi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n valea hot<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rii: c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci Ziua Domnului e aproape <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n valea hot<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rii. Soarele <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i luna se vor <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntuneca, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i stelele <text:span text:style-name="T5">îº</text:span>i vor ascunde str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lucirea. <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i Domnul va striga afar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> din Sion, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i-<text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a glasul din Ierusalim; <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cerurile <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul se vor cl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tina: iar Domnul va fi puterea poporului s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u”.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Hristos a spus:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„<text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>ndat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> tulbur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile acelor zile, soarele se va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntuneca, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i luna nu va mai lumina, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i stelele vor c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>dea din cer semnul Fiului Omului: <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i atunci toate triburile de pe p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt se vor jeli <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i vor vedea pe Fiul Omului venind pe norii cerului, cu putere <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i mare slav<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>”. - Matei XXIV, 29,30.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>ar <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Qur’<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>n citim:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">C<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd va fi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>luit soarele,</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd vor c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>dea stelele, <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd se vor n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rui mun<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii,</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd se vor desf<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>ura filele C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii,</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd se va descoperi Cerul </text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd se va aprinde focul iadului”. -Surat XXXI.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Cartea Iq<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>n, l<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>mure<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> aceste profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii, privitoare la soare, lun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i stele, la cer <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i la p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, sunt simbolice <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i nu trebuie <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elese <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n sensul literal. Profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nainte de toate, d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>deau <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsemn<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tate tuturor lucrurilor spirituale, nu celor materiale; lumii spirituale, nu celei fizice. C<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd pomenesc de soare, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n leg<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cu Ziua Judec<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii, se refer<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> la Soarele Drept<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii. Soarele supremul izvor de lumin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>; Moise, bun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>oar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, a fost un soare pentru evrei, precum a fost Hristos pentru cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tini <t