    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul „nor” <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nseamn<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> lucrurile ce se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpotrivesc egoismului <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i dorin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elor omene<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti, pomene<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>torul verset: „A<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>adar, voi, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd vor veni soli, aduc<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd ceea ce nu doresc sufletele voastre, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-i izgoni<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i cu trufie, pe al<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nvinui<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i de f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþã</text:span>rnicie <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pe al<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-i ucide<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i”. (Qur’<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>n S. II). Asemenea nori sunt de pild<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, schimbarea poruncilor, prefacerea legilor, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>turarea r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nduielilor <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a ceremoniilor obi<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>nuite, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ridicarea poporului de jos, care ajunge credincios, deasupra <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:st