    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Precum norii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpiedic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ochii omului s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> privesc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fenomenul soarelui, tot astfel, st<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile de mai sus, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpiedic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pe popor, de a pricepe Soarele Ideal... Deoarece, aceste Temple ale Sfin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>eniei, erau supuse la tulbur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri exterioare ca s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cia <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i nenorocirea, precum <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i la nevoi fire<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i trupe<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti, ca foamea, setea <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i alte deosebite <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mpl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri, poporul ar r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n pustiuri de <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndoial<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de b<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>nuieli, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n de<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>erturi de <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nchipuiri <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i nedumeriri, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntreb<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndu-se: „Cum se po