    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Potrivit cu l<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>muririle de mai sus, venirea Fiului Omului, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n smerit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntruchipare omeneasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>scut din femeie, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rac, f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> carte, prigonit <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i asuprit de puternicii p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntului - acest chip al venirii Lui, e chiar piatra de <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncercare, prin mijlocul c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>reia, judec<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> popoarele de pe p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i le deosebe<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te unul de altul, cum desparte un p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>stor, oile de <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>api. Cei, ai c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ror ochi spirituali sunt deschi<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i, pot p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>trunde ace<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti nori <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i se pot bucura de „puterea <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i marea slav<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>”, - adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rata slav<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a lui Dumnezeu - pe care vine s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ne-o dezv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>luie; ceilal<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, ai c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ror ochi, sunt <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> tulbura<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i de eroare <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de prejudecat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, nu pot vedea dec<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t norul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntunecos, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i b<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>jb<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ie necontenit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n umbr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, lipsi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i de binecuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntata str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lucire a soarelui.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> voi trimite solul meu, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i va preg<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ti calea, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>naintea mea: iar Dumnezeul, pe care <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>l c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>uta<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, va veni nea<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>teptat <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n templul lui, chiar solul legii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntru care v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> bucura<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Dar cine poate a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tepta ziua sosirii Lui? <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i cine va r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ne <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n picioare c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd se va ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ta El? C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci El e ca focul topitorului <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ca le<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ia n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lbitorului...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci, iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, vine ziua, care va arde ca un cuptor; <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i cei trufa<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i cei r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>i, vor fi ca miri<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tea. Ziua care vine <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>i va arde zice Domnul o<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tirilor, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i nu le va l<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sa nici r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nici ramur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Dar pentru voi, care v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> teme<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, de numele Meu, va r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri Soarele Drept<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii, cu t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duire <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n aripile Lui”. - Mal. III.IV.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T21">Not</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">ã</text:span>. - Subiectul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeplinirii profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iilor, este at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t de <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntins, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t ar trebui multe volume, pentru a-l trata cum se cuvine. Tot ce se poate face, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n limitele unui singur capitol, e a indica pe scurt liniile generale, a interpret<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rilor Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>. Am<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>nuntele Apocalipse dest<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>inuite de Daniel <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de Sf. Ioan, au r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>mas neatinse aici. Cititorii vor g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>si unele capitole <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T21">R</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">spunsuri la c</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">â</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">teva </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">î</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">ntreb</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">ri</text:span> (vezi bibliografia), <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T21">Cartea </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T21">Iq</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">á</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">n</text:span>, de Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, <text:span text:style-name="T21">Dovezi Bah</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">á</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">’</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">í</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">,</text:span> de Mirza ‘Abu’l-Fadl, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n multe din Scrisorile lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ale lui ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, se pot g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>si <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i alte t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ciri ale profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iilor lor.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">CAPITOLUL XIV</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">PROFE<text:span text:style-name="T5">Þ</text:span>IILE LUI BAH<text:span text:style-name="T5">Á</text:span>’U’LL<text:span text:style-name="T5">Á</text:span>H <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>I ALE LUI ‘ABDU’L-BAH<text:span text:style-name="T5">Á</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Iar dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> vei zice <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n inima ta, cum s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tim cuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul, pe care Dumnezeu nu l-a rostit? C<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd vorbe<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te un profet <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n numele Domnului, dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> acel lucru nu urmeaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i nu se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mpl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, e un lucru pe care Dumnezeu, nu l-a rostit, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pe care l-a spus cu prea mult<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zneal<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> profetul: s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu te temi de el”. - Deut. XVIII.22 (Motto).</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T22">Puterea Creatoare a Cuv</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">â</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">ntului lui Dumnezeu.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Dumnezeu, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Dumnezeu singur, are puterea s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> oricevrea, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cea mai mare dovad<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> un om e o Manifestare a lui Dumnezeu, e puterea creatoare a cuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntului Lui - <text:s/><text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i darul Lui de a transforma <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de a preschimba toate lucrurile omene<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nvinge orice <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpotrivire omeneasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Dumnezeu <text:span text:style-name="T5">îº</text:span>i veste<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te voin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a, prin cuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ilor Lui, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mplinirea grabnic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> sau mai t<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rzie a acelor cuvinte, e cea mai limpede dovad<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a menirii profetului <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rului inspira<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iei lui.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci, precum ploaia <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i z<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>pada se coboar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> din cer, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i nu se mai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntorc acolo, ci ud<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>l face s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> rodeasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> odr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sleasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pentru ca s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> dea s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> sem<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>torului <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ine celui ce m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, tot a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Cuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul Meu, care iese din gura Mea, nu se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntoarce la Mine f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> rod, ci va face voia Mea <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mplini planurile Mele”. - Isa. LV,10,11.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">C<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd au venit discipolii lui Ioan Botez<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>torul la Iisus s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-l <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntrebe: „E<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti tu, acel ce trebuia s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> vin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, ori trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tept<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m pe altul?” Iisus n-a dat alt r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>spuns ci a ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tat urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile cuvintelor Lui:</text:p>
