    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n anul 1869, Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h scrise lui Napoleon al III-lea, mustr<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndu-l pentru pofta lui de r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zboi, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pentru dispre<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ul cu care <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mpinase o scrisoare mai veche a lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h. Scrisoare cuprinde urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toarele aspre amenin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>ri:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Faptele tale, vor arunca <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ia ta <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n tulbur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri, domnia va trece din m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>inile tale, ca consecin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> a faptelor tale <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i astfel vei suferi o grozav<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pierdere. Fr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri vor cuprinde popoarele din acea <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> dep<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rtat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu te ridici <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ap<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rarea acestei cauze, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu urmezi Duhul, pe o cale dreapt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. M<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rirea ta te-a f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cut seme<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>? Pe via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a mea! Ea nu va d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>inui, ba mai mult <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, se va n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rui, dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu te <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii str<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ns de aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> puternic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> funie. Noi vedem <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nfr<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ngerea, fug<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rindu-te din urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci e<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti dintre acei ce sunt nechibzui<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i”.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">E de prisos s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> mai spunem, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Napoleon, care era atunci la apogeul puterii lui, n-a luat <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n seam<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> prevestire. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n anul urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tor, intr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zboi cu Prusia, convins c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> trupele lui, u<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>or vor cuceri Berlinul; <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nenorocirea prevestit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zu asupra lui. Fu <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nvins la Saarbruck, la Weissenburg, la Metz, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-o strivitoare catastrof<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> la Sedan. Fu atunci luat prizonier <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Prusia, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i doi ani dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> aceea, muri nefericit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Anglia.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P20">Germania.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h mai t<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rziu, f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cu o prevestire tot at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t de solemn<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nving<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>torilor lui Napoleon, care c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zu <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n urechi surde, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i fu urmat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> mai t<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rziu, de o cumplit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeplinire. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T21">Cartea Aqdas</text:span>, care a fost <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceput<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> la Adrianopole, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n primii ani ai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntemni<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>rii lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h la Akk<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, scrise <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ratului Germaniei, precum urmeaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„O rege al Berlinului!... Adu-<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i aminte de cel ce era mai presus dec<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t tine, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rire (Napoleon III) <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i al c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rei treapt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> era mai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nalt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> dec<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t a ta. Unde e el acum? <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i unde sunt avu<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iile lui? Ia aminte <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i nu fii din acei ce dorm. El a aruncat la spate Scrisoarea Domnului, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd i-am f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cut cunoscut ce ni se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mplase de pe urma o<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tirilor asupritoare <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i astfel l-a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpresurat din toate p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ile nenorocorea, p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd s-a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntors <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, cu mari pierderi. O, Rege, cuget<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ad<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nc asupra lui, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i asupra celor ce sunt ca tine, care au cucerit cet<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>i, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i au domnit asupra robilor Domnului - iar Dumnezeu i-a scobor<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t din palat <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n morm<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt. Ia aminte <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i fii din cei ce sunt cu chibzuial<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">O Maluri, ale R<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ului Rin! V-am v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zut muiate <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n s<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nge, pentru c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> s-au tras <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpotriva voastr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>biile r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>spl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i are s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> vie r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc-odat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i noi auzim <text:soft-page-break/>jelirea Berlinului, cu toate c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> azi, se afl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n mare slav<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>”.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n timpul izb<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nzilor germane, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Marele R<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zboi, de la 1914-18, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i mai ales <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n timpul ultimei ofensive a Germaniei, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n prim<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>var<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> anului 1918, aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> binecunoscut<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ie, era citat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i potrivnicii Mi<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Persia pentru a discredita pe Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h: dar c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd av<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul victorios al <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>naint<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii germane, s-a preschimbat deodat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n strivire, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n cumplit dezastru, str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ele du<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>manilor Cauzei Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>, se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntorseser<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> asupra lor <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ile, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i marea r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sp<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndire ce o d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duser<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iilor, ajunse un mijloc puternic de a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri faima lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P20">Persia.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n Cartea Aqdas, scris<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd tiranicul <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>ah Muzaffaru’d-Din Sh<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h era <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n culmea puterii, Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h binecuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nteaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ora<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ul Teheran, care e capitala Persiei, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i locul na<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>terii lui, zic<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„O, <text:span text:style-name="T5">Þ</text:span>ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a lui T<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span> (Teheran)! Nu fii at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t de <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndurerat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> din vreo pricin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Dumnezeu a f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cut din tine locul unde r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sar Zorile Bucuriei lumii. De va fi voia Lui, va binecuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nta tronul t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u cu unul care va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i cu dreptate <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i va aduna laolalt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> oile Domnului, risipite de lupi. Cu adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat, va d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rui poporului lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, bucurie <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i veselie. Iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, el e din esen<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a poporului, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ochii lui Dumnezeu...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Bucur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-te, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci Dumnezeu a f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cut din tine, o Zare de Lumin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, pentru c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n tine s-a n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>scut R<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ritul Zorilor Manifest<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii... <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n cur<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd se vor schimba <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n tine or<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nduielile, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i va domni asupra ta, o republic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a oamenilor. Cu adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat St<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nul t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u e Cel <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elept, Cel Atotcuprinz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tor. Fii sigur de buna ocrotire a St<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nului t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u. Cu adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat, Chipul Milostivirii, nu va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceta de a te privi, cu Ochii Dragostei. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n cur<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd, se va s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>lui <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n tine, pacea dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> tulbur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri (<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>eala din haos). Astfel a fost ursit, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Cartea Minunilor”.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">P<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> acum Persia abia a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceput s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ias<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> din starea de tulburare prevestit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, dar s-a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceput de pe acum, un guvern constitu<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ional <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i nu lipsesc semnele c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se va deschide <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n cur<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd o er<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> mai str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lucit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Turcia.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, pe atunci <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nchis <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-o temni<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> turceasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n 1868) scrise Sultanului Turciei <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Ministrului s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u, ‘Ali Pa<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a, o scrisoare cuprinz<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd cele mai solemne <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsemnate prevestiri.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:soft-page-break/>Sultanului <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>i scrise din cazarma de la ‘Akk<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„O, tu, care te socote<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti cel mai mare dintre to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i oamenii... <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n scurt timp, numele t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u va fi uitat, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i te vei afla <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n mare cump<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rerea ta, acest <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>nvior<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tor al lumii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ciuitorul ei, e vinovat <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zvr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tit. Ce nelegiuire au f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ptuit, femeile, copiii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pruncii neputincio<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i, pentru a fi vrednici de <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nver<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>unarea ta? Ai prigonit un mare num<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r de fiin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>e, care n-au ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tat nici o <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpotrivire <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ara noastr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i care n-au pus la cale, nici o r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zvr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tire <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpotriva guvernului t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u; ba mai degrab<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, s-au <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeletnicit ziua <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i noaptea, cu pa<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>nica pomenire a lui Dumnezeu. Le-ai jefuit avutul, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i prin faptele tale tiranice, li s-a luat tot ce era al lor... <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n ochii lui Dumnezeu, o m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> plin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de <text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> e mai mare, dec<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t toat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ia, slava, suveranitatea <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rirea ta <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ar vrea, te-ar risipi ca nisipul din pustiu. Peste pu<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>in, te va lovi m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nia Lui, se vor isca r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zvr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tiri, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>rile tale vor fi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ite!</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Atunci vei pl<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nge <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i te vei jeli, dar nic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ieri, nu vei g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>si ajutor sau ocrotire... Ia seama, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nia lui Dumnezeu e preg<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:s/>peste pu<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>in vei vedea, cele ce au fost scrise, de Pana Poruncii”. (vezi Steaua Apusului, vol. II p.3).</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Iar lui ‘Ali Pa<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a, iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce i-a scris:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„O, Ra’is (<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ef) ai f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ptuit cele ce au f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cut pe Mahomed, profetul lui Dumnezeu, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> geam<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Supremul Paradis. Lumea te-a f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cut seme<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t te-ai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntors de la Fa<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a cu a c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rei Str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lucire au fost luminate popoarele din Adun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile Cere<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n cur<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd te vei afla, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n net<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> sc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>dere. Te-ai unit cu St<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nul Persiei, pentru a-mi face r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u, cu toate c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> venisem la tine, din Locul unde r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sar Zorile Celui Atotputernic, Celui Mare, cu o Pricin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> care <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nviora ochii ale<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ilor lui Dumnezeu...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Ai crezut c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> vei putea stinge focul, pe care Dumnezeu l-a aprins <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n lume? Nu! O declar pe Sufletul Lui cel Adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat, dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ai fi dintre cei ce <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>eleg. Ba mai mult <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, prin cele ce-ai f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ptuit, s-a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nte<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>it <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, vlv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>taia fl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rilor lui. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n cur<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd va cuprinde lumea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntreag<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pe locuitorii ei. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n cur<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd, <text:span text:style-name="T5">Þ</text:span>ara Misterului (adic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Adrianopole) <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i alte <text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>ri, vor fi schimbate, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i vor trece din m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>inile Regilor, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i se vor ivi tulbur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri, se vor auzi gemete, corup<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ia se va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntinde <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n toate <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>inuturile, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i toate treburile se vor <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncurca, din pricina chipului cum au fost asupri<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i priznierii (Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i tovar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>ii lui) de c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tre mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>imea prigonitoare. St<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nirea va fi schimbat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i starea <text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>rii se va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ut<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t se vor jeli nisipurile <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i dealurile p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>site, pomii vor v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rsa lacrimi pe mun<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i va curge s<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nge din toate locurile, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i va vedea poporul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n mare nenorocire...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Astfel s-au hot<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t lucrurile de c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tre Cel Hot<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>tor, Cel <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elept, la a c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rui Porunc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu se pot <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpotrivi o<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tirile cerului <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ale p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntului, nici nu-l pot opri, de la Voia Lui, regii <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rmuitorii. Nenorocirile sunt untdelemnul acestei L<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>mpi, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i prin ele i se m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>re<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te Lumina, numai de-ai fi, dintre cei ce <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>eleg! Toate <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpotrivirile ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tate de <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpilatori, sunt ca ni<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te crainici <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> privin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci <text:soft-page-break/>prin ei, s-a r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sp<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndit larg, printre popoarele lumii Ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tarea lui Dumnezeu, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Cauza Lui”. </text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Iar <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Cartea Aqdas, a scris:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„O, Punct ce te afli, pe malul celor dou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri (adic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Contantinopolul)! Tronul nedrept<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii a fost statornicit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n tine, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n tine s-a aprins focul urii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a chip <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t, Oastea Suprem<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se t<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nguie din pricina ei, precum <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cei ce stau roat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n jurul <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>naltului Tron. Noi privim <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n tine, pe cel f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> minte, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rmuind peste cel <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elept <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntunericul crez<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndu-se mai presus dec<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t Lumina, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r tu e<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>dit, st<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nit de trufie.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Oare, podoabele tale exterioare, te-au f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cut trufa<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>? <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n cur<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd vei pieri, pe St<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nul Crea<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iei! <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i se vor t<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ngui fiicele <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duvele, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i toate fiin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ele ce sunt <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ia ta. Astfel, <text:span text:style-name="T5">îþ</text:span>i porunce<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te, Cel <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elept, Cel Atot<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tiutor!”.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Nenorocirile succesive, care s-au ab<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tut asupra acestei <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii odinioar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>re<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>e, de la publicarea acestor prevestiri, au comentat <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n chip destul de uimitor, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elesul lor profetic.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P20">America.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n Cartea Aqdas, scris<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> acum vreo cincizeci de ani, Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u;ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h a trimis Americii, urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>torul apel:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„O, voi C<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rmuitori ai Americii, Pre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>edin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Guvernatori ai Republicii ei ... Asculta<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i chemarea, din Locul Rev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rsatului Zorilor pe <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>imi: nu e alt Dumnezeu dec<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t Mine, Cel ce gr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ie<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i e Atot<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tiutor: Cu m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>inile drept<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii, lega<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>dularul cel fr<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cu varga Poruncii, Dumnezeului vostrul Cel Puternic, Cel <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elept fr<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nge<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>dularele s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toase ale asupritorilor!”.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n conferin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ele sale din America <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i din alte locuri <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i-a rostit adesea rug<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>mintea precum <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>dejdea <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncrederea, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> America, cea dint<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>i, va <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a stindardul p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cii interna<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ionale.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">La Cincinatti, Ohio, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n 5 noiembrie 1912, a spus urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toarele:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„America e o <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nobil<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, purt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toarea stindardului p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n lumea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntreag<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i-a rev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rsat lumina peste toate religiile. Alte na<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iuni, ca Statele Unite nu sunt desc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ate <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i libere de uneltiri de aceea nu sunt <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n stare s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nf<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ptuiasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Pacea Universal<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Dar America, Slav<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Domnului, e <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n pace cu lumea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntreag<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i e vrednic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a steagul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nfr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>irii <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cii <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntre oameni. C<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd se va ridica din America, chemarea c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tre Pacea Universal<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, toat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> omenirea va striga: „Da primim.” <text:soft-page-break/>Neamurile, din toate climele se vor uni pentru a primi <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþã</text:span>turile lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, care au fpst revelate, acum cincizeci de ani. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n Scrisorile Lui, a cerut tuturor parlamentelor din lume, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i trimit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> membrii cei mai buni <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cei mai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elep<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i la un parlament al lumii <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntregi, care s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> hot<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> asupra tuturor ne<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elegerilor dintre popoare <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> statorniceasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pacea... atunci vom avea Parlamentul Omului, pe care l-au visat profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii.” - Steaua Apusului, vol VI, p.81.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Chem<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i-au primit de pe acum, r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>spuns, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-o larg<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Statele Unite ale Americii <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n nici o <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> din lume, nu au fost primite cu at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ta bun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>voin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþã</text:span>turile Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>. Rolul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncredin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>at Americii, de a chema toate neamurile la pacea interna<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ional<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, nu a fost <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mplinit p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> acum, dec<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n mod par<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ial <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>i, a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>teapt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cu <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsufle<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ire, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mpl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile ce au s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se mai iveasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n viitor.</text:p>
