    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span> au prevestit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n mai multe r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nduri, cu uimitoare precizie, izbucnirea Marelui R<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zboi din 1914 - 18. La Sacramento, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n California, la 26 octombrie 1912, iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce a spus ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„<text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n ziua de azi, continentul European, e ca un arsenal. E un depozit de materii explozibile, care a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>teapt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> numai o sc<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nteie, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i o singur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> sc<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nteie ar putea s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> dea foc, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntregii europe, mai ales acum, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd se dezbate chestiunea Balcanilor.”</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Rosti asemenea prevestiri, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n multe conferin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>e <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>inute <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n America <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Europa. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n alt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> conferin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> rostita <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n California, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n octombrie 1912, iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce a spus:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Suntem <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ajunul b<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>liei de la Armagheddon, de care se pomene<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n capitolul al <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>aisprezecelea din Apocalips<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Mai sunt numai doi ani p<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> dea foc o sc<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nteie <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntregii Europe.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Nelini<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tea social<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> din toate <text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>rile, necredin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a religioas<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> din ce <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ce mai mare, premerg<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toare unui mileniu, care e de pe acum <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nceput, vor da foc <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntregii Europe, a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a cum e proroocit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Cartea lui Daniel <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Cartea (Apocalipsa) lui Ioan.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n 1917, se vor n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rui <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ra<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cataclisme vor cutremura p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntul.” - (Men<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ionat de Mrs. Corinne True <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Revista North Shore, 26 septembrie 1914, Chicago, U.S.A.).</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n ajunul marelui r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zboi, a spus urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toarele:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Se apropie o <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ierare general<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, a tuturor neamurilor civilizate. O nemaipomenit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> lupt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se preg<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>te<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te. Lumea e <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n pragul celei mai tragice r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zboiri. Nenum<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rate o<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tiri - milioane de oameni - se mobilizeaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i se adun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de-a lungul grani<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elor. Se preg<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tesc pentru <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nfrico<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ata b<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>t<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lie. Cea mai mic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pricin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>i va azv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rli <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-o ciocnire f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> seam<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i are s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se i<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te o conflagra<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ie, a c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rei pereche <text:soft-page-break/>nu s-a mai v<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zut, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n trecuta istorie a neamului omenesc.” - (la Haifa, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n 3 august, 1914) - Steaua Apusului, vol.V, p.163.</text:p>
