    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T39">„Dumnezeu a trimis durerea, ca o ploaie de diminea</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">þã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T39">, pe o p</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">ãº</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T39">une verde, ca u fitil pentru Lampa Lui, prin care se lumineaz</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T39"> cerul </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">º</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T39">i p</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T39">m</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">â</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T39">ntul... Prin durere a str</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T39">lucit Lumina Lui, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">º</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T39">i Lauda Lui, n-a </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">î</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T39">ncetat de a radia; acesta a fost modul lui de a lucra, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">î</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T39">n toate veacurile </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">º</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T39">i </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T19">î</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T39">n vremea de demult.”</text:span></text:p>
