    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Starea lumii de azi, ne d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> o dovad<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndestul<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>toare c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> afar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de rare excep<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii, oamenii din toate religiile au nevoie de a fi <text:s/>rede<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tepta<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, pentru a-<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i da seama de adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ratul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>eles al religiei lor; aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> re-de<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>teptare, e o parte <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsemnat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, a operei lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h. El a venit, ca s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pe Cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tini, Cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tini mai buni, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> din Musulmani adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ra<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i Musulmani, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pe to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i oamenii s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> asculte de duhul, care a inspirat pe profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii lor. De asemeni, El <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpline<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duiala dat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i acei profe<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, cu privire la o mai str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lucit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Manifestare, care avea s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se iveasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, la „<text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>mplinirea Timpului”, pentru a des<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>v<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncorona lucrarea. El desf<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>oar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rurile spirituale, mai deplin dec<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t predecesorii lui, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ne dest<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>inuie<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te Voin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a lui Dumnezeu, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n privin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a tuturor problemelor vie<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii individuale <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i sociale, care ne <text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mpin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n lumea de azi.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Ne d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> un <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt universal, pe a c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rei neclintit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> temelie se poate cl<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>di o civiliza<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ie mai bun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>; un <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt potrivit cu nevoile lumii <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n noua er<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, care <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncepe acum.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Nevoia unei noi Revela<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Unificarea omenirii <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntregi, topirea la un loc a diferitelor religii ale lumii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mp<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>carea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntre Religie <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>tiin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>, statornicirea unei P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci Universale, a unui Arbitraj Interna<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ional, a unei Case a Drept<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii Interna<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ionale, a unei Limbi Interna<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ionale, Emanciparea Femeii, Educa<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ie Universal<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, abolirea Sclaviei nu numai Individuale ci <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Industriale, Organizarea Omenirii ca un singur tot, f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a nesocoti drepturile fiec<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rui individ - astea sunt probleme de o m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>re<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ie uria<text:span text:style-name="T5">ºã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de o nemaipomenit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> greutate, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n privin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rora, Cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tinii, Mahomedanii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i credincio<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ii altor religii, au avut <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i au <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> vederile cele mai felurite <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>teodat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cr<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ncen potrivnice, Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, a statornicit limpede, principii hot<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>te, care de ar fi pretutindeni <text:span text:style-name="T21">adoptate</text:span>, ar face din lume un rai.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T22">Adev</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">rul e al tuturor.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i sunt gata s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> admit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sp<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndirea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntului Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>, ar fi un lucru foarte folositor pentru Persia <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>rile din R<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rit, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">îº</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nchipuiesc, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu se potrive<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te cu <text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>rile Apusene <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> acestea n-au nevoie de ele.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce a r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>spuns ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, unei persoane, care exprima aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rere:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„<text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n ceea ce prive<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elesul Mi<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>, orice se atinge de binele universal, e de la Dumnezeu, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i orice e de la Dumnezeu, e spre binele ob<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tesc. Ce e adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat, e adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat pentru to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i; dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu e adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat, nu e bun pentru nimeni; de aceea, pricina divin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a unui bine universal, nu poate fi m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rginit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> numai pentru Apus, sau pentru R<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rit, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci razele Soarelui Adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rului,lumineaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Orientul <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Occidentul, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">îº</text:span>i trimit c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ldura <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i la Nord <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i la Sud - nu e deosebire <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntre un pol <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i altul. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n timpul Manifest<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii lui Hristos, Romanii <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Grecii credeau, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> credin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a Lui, se potrive<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te numai pentru Evrei. - Ei credeau c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> au o civiliza<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ie des<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>v<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu au nimic de inv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþã</text:span>t de la preceptele Cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tine, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i din pricina acestei <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nchipuiri gre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ite, mul<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i au fost lipsi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i de Harul Lui Hristos. De asemenea, afla<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> principiile Cre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tine <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Poruncile lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, sunt identice <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile lor, acelea<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n fiecare zi, se <text:soft-page-break/>des<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>v<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>e<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te progresul; a fost o vreme c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> divin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> institu<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ie ( a revela<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iei progresive) era numai embrion, apoi a fost prunc, a poi copil, apoi t<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r copt la minte; iar ast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zi, str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>luce<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te de frumuse<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>e <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i radiaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> o nespus<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> lumin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Fericit cel ce p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>trunde misterul, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">îº</text:span>i ia locul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n lumea celor minuna<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i”.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">TESTAMENTUL <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>I ULTIMELE DORIN<text:span text:style-name="T5">Þ</text:span>E ALE LUI ‘ABDU’L-BAH<text:span text:style-name="T5">Á</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Faza cea nou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Cu trecerea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n alt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> lume, a iubitului ei conduc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tor, ‘abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, Mi<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>carea Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>, a intrat, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-o nou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> faz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a istoriei ei. Crescuse at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t era nevoie de o organiza<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ie mai sitematic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, pentru a r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndui, lucr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile prietenilor ei <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n toate p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ile lumii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pentru a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nf<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ptui o mai mare unitate <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i for<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> de propagare. Planul de organizare, fisese dinainte schi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>at de Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, dar a fost desf<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>urat mai am<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>nun<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>it <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Testamentul <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Ultimele dorin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>e ale lui ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>. Cele trei puncte mai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsemnate din Testament, sunt:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">1. „P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zitorulul Cauzei lui Dumnezeu”,</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">2. „M<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>inile Cauzei lui Dumnezeu” <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">3. „Adun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile Spirituale, Locale, Na<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ionale <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Interna<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ionale”.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T22">P</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">zitorul Cauzei lui Dumnezeu.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, a ales pe cel mai mare dintre nepo<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii lui, Shoghi Effendi, pentru slujba plin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>spundere de „P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zitor al Cauzei” (Val<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>y<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>-Amru’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h).</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Shoghi Effendi, e fiul cel mai mare al lui Z<text:span text:style-name="T5">íáá</text:span>yy<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h Hk<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>num, fiica cea mai mare a lui ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>. Tat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u, M<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>rz<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span> H<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>d<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>, e <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nrudit cu B<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>b (cu toate c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu e un urma<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span> direct al lui, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci singurul fiu al lui B<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>b, a murit de copil). Shoghi Effendi era de dou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zeci <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cinci de ani, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i studia la Balliol College, din Oxford, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd trecu bunicul-s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a cealalt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> cum roste<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, alegerea lui Shoghi, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Testamentul s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„O, prietenii mei iubitori; dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce va trece <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n alt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>, acest n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>stuit, se cuvine ca Ramurile <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i L<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>starii Pomului Sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt, (adic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> rudele lui B<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>b <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ale lui Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h precum <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i M<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>inile Cauzei lui Dumnezeu, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cei iubi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i de Binecuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntata Frumuse<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>e, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntoarc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nspre Shoghi Effendi, - t<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ra Ramur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> din Am<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndoi Pomii Sfin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Binecuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nta<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, (B<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>b <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h) e un rod crescut din <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpreunarea a dou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ml<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>di<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>e din Pomul Sfin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>eniei; c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci el e semnul lui Dumnezeu, Ramura cea Aleas<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zitorul Cauzei lui Dumnezeu <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cei iubi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i de d<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nsul, trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntoarc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. El e l<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>muritorul Cuvintelor lui Dumnezeu, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> el va urma, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>iul <text:soft-page-break/>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>scut, dintre urma<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ii lui direc<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i...</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Ramura t<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zitorul Cauzei lui Dumnezeu, precum <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i Adunarea Ob<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>teasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> (Baytu’l-Adl) care trebuie aleas<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntemeiat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, sunt sub grija <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ocrotirea Binecuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntatei Frumuse<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, sub paza <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rmuirea ne<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ov<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ielnic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, a Sfin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iei Sale, Cel Prea <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>nalt. Fie via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a mea jertfit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pentru ei am<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndoi! Orice vor hot<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span> ei, e de la Dumnezeu.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">O, voi cei iubi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i de Domnul! Se cuvine ca P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zitorul Cauzei lui Dumnezeu, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> aleag<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n timpul vie<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii lui pe cel ce-i va fi urma<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>, ca s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>mple ne<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elegeri, dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> trecerea lui, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n alt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>. Cel ce va fi ales, trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> arate <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsul dezrobire de cele p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nte<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti, trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fie chintesen<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a cur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>iei, trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> dovedeasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fric<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de Dumnezeu, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tiin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elepciune <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nv<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþã</text:span>tur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Astfel, dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> primul-n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>scut al P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zitorului Cauzei lui Dumnezeu, n-ar ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ta <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsul adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rul cuvintelor, „Fiul este tainica esen<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> a p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rintelui s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u”, adic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> n-ar mo<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>teni ceea ce era spiritual <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n tat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>u, (P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zitorul) <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i dac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> m<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rea<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a lui ob<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ie nu s-ar <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nvedera <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-o fire aleas<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, atunci trebuie ca P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zitorul Cauzei lui Dumnezeu, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> aleag<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> drept urma<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>, alt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Ramur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">M<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>inile Cauzei lui Dumnezeu, trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> numeasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> dintre d<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ii, nou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ale<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i, a c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ror <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeletnicire <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n tot timpul, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fie de a ajuta <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsemnata sa menire, pe P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zitorul Cauzei lui Dumnezeu. Alegerea acestor nou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fie <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntemeiat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pe unanimitate sau pe majoritate, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n adunarea M<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>inilor Cauzei lui Dumnezeu, iar ace<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tia, trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i dea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nvoirea, fie prin unanimitate, fie prin majoritate, pentru <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rirea celui pe care P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zitorul Cauzei lui Dumnezeu, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i l-a ales urma<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>. Aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nvoire trebuie dat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n a<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>a chip, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu se <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tie care voci <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i-au dat votul pentru <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i care <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i l-au dat contra (adic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> prin vot secret)”.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T22">„M</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">â</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">inile Cauzei lui Dumnezeu”.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n timpul vie<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ii sale, Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h, a ales patru prieteni credincio<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncerca<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i, pentru a ajuta la <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndrumarea <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sp<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndirea Mi<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i le-a dat numele de Ay<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>d<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>yi-Amru’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h (<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntraducere literal<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> „M<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>inile Cauzei lui Dumnezeu”). Trei, dintre ei, au trecut <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-alt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i numai unul a r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>mas. ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, hot<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãº</text:span>te <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Testamentul lui, alc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tuirea unei grup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri statornice, menite s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> slujeasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Cauza <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ajute pe P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zitorul Cauzei lui Dumnezeu, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i care s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> poarte acela<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i nume.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce scrie:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„O, prieteni,! M<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>inile Cauzei lui Dumnezeu, trebuie numite <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i alese de P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zitorul <text:soft-page-break/>Cauzei lui Dumnezeu... Menirea M<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>inilor Cauzei lui Dumnezeu, e de a r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sp<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndi Binecuv<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntata Mireasm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, de a <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a sufletele oamenilor, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de a fi, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n tot timpul, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n toate <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mprejur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile, sfin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ite <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i dezlegate de cele p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nte<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>ti.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> arate frica de Dumnezeu <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n purtarea lor, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n apuc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>turile, faptele <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i cuvintele lor.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Grupul M<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>inilor Cauzei lui Dumnezeu, e sub c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>rmuirea P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zitorului Cauzei lui Dumnezeu. El e dator s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-i <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndemne <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duiasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> dup<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> toate puterile lor, pentru a r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sp<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndi dulcea mireasm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> a lui Dumnezeu, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i pentru a c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>uzi toate popoarele din lume, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ci str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>lucirea Divinei C<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>l<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>uziri, a adus <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntregului univers, lumin<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T22">Adun</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">rile spirituale.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Adun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile Spirituale Locale, ale Mi<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>, au fost descrise <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n alt capitol i se <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>in <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n timpul de fa<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n multe p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i ale lumii. <text:span text:style-name="T5">Î</text:span>n afar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de ele, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’u’ll<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>h <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, au r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nduit alc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tuirea unor adun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri spirituale, na<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ionale <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i interna<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ionale.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Iat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ce scrie ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Testamentul lui:</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">„Iar acum, <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n ceea ce prive<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te Adunarea (Baytu’l-‘Adl) pe care Dumnezeu, a poruncit ca izvor al binelui <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i dezb<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de orice gre<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>eal<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fie aleas<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> prin sufragiu universal, i anume de c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tre credincio<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i.Membrii ei, trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fie manifest<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri a fricei de Dumnezeu, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rit de zori ai <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elepciunii <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ai cuno<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>tin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ei, trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fie statornici <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Credin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a lui Dumnezeu, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i binevoitori, fa<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> de omenirea <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntreag<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>. Aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> adunare, este cea universal<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n fiece <text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, trebuie alc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tuit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> o alt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> adunare par<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ial<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i aceste Adun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ri par<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iale, trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> aleag<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> membrii celei Universale, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>reia trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> i se supun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> toate chestiunile. Ea <text:span text:style-name="T21">hot</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">ã</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">r</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T7">ãº</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T21">te</text:span> toate legile <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i regulamentele, care nu se g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>sesc explicit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Textul Sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt. Tot aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> adunare, trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> dezlege orice problem<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> grea, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i P<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>zitorul Cauzei lui Dumnezeu, e sfin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>ita ei c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>petenie <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i e pe via<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>, cel mai presus dintre to<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i membrii adun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii. C<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nd nu e de fa<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> la deliber<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile ei, trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> numeasc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> pe cineva care s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>-l reprezinte... Aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> Adunare, emite legile, trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ajute <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> sprijine adunarea legislativ<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, astfel <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nc<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t, prin str<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nsa unire <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i colaborare a acestor dou<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> puteri, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ajung<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> neclintit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i puternic<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, temelia drept<text:span text:style-name="T5">ãþ</text:span>ii <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a nep<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rtinirii, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se prefac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> toate col<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>urile p<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ntului <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntr-un adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat Rai.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Fiecare trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ia sfat de la Cartea Cea Prea Sfin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>it<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i orice nu se va g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>si, am<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>nun<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>it l<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>murit <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n cuprinsul ei, trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fie supus Adun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii Universale. Orice va hot<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span> aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> adunare, fie prin unanimitate, fie prin majoritate de voturi, e net<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>g<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duit adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i e voia lui Dumnezeu. Ori<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>icine se dep<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rteaz<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de aceste <text:soft-page-break/>hot<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ri, e <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r, dintre cei ce iubesc dezbinarea, ce arat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> rea voin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i-au <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ntors fa<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>a de la Dumnezeul Legii.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">E datoria membrilor, (Adun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii Universale) s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> se adune laolalt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> ia <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n cercetare toate problemele, care au pricinuit ne<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elegeri, toate chestiunile nel<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>murite, sau care nu sunt am<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>nun<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>it expuse <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Carte. Orice va hot<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span> adunarea, are tot at<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ta putere ca <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i textul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i. <text:span text:style-name="T5">ª</text:span>i precum Adunarea are putere s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> promulge legi, care nu sunt pomenite <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n Carte, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i care privesc tranzac<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>iile zilnice, tot astfel, are puterea s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> revoce acele legi. Astfel, buno<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>oar<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, Adunarea a promulgat azi, o lege oarecare, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a dispus <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ndeplinirea ei, iar peste o sut<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> de ani, schimb<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>ndu-se <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mprejur<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rile, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i starea de lucruri fiind diferit<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, o alt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> adunare va avea atunci puterea s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> schimbe acea lege, potrivit cu nevoile vremii. Aceasta, poate s-o fac<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, pentru c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> legea nu f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>cea parte, din Divinul Text explicit. Adunarea este totodat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>, f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>uritoarea <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i revocatoarea propriilor ei legi”.</text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T22">Alte fragmente din Testamentul lui ‘Adbu’l-Bah</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T9">á</text:span><text:span text:style-name="T22">.</text:span></text:p>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10"/>
    <text:p text:style-name="P10">Fiind dat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsemn<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tatea f<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> seam<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>n a Testamentului <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i a Ultimelor Dorin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>e ale lui ‘Abdu’l-Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>, gravitatea urm<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rilor lor, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i ad<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nca <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>elepciune ascuns<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n cuprinsul lor, ne d<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m seama, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> nu ar fi locul <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n momentul de fa<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>, s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ncerc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>m, a face asupra lor, vreun comentariu. Totu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i, vom da ca un sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it potrivit la aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> schi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> a Mi<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>c<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rii Bah<text:span text:style-name="T5">á</text:span>’<text:span text:style-name="T5">í</text:span>, alte c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>teva fragmente, care zugr<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>vesc, c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t se poate de limpede, spiritul <te