    <text:p text:style-name="P10">O, voi, cei iubi<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>i de Domnul! <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n aceast<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> sf<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>nt<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> „Alc<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>tuire” nu sunt <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>ng<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>duite c<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>tu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i de pu<text:span text:style-name="T5">þ</text:span>in vrajba <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i dezbinarea. Fiece <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>mpilator, se lipse<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>te pe el <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>nsu<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i, de harul lui Dumnezeu. E datoria fiec<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ruia s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> arate cea mai des<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>v<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>r<text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>it<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> iubire, neprih<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>nire <text:span text:style-name="T5">î</text:span>n purtare, sinceritate <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i adev<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>rat<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> bun<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>voin<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span>, fa<text:span text:style-name="T5">þã</text:span> de toate popoarele, <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i neamurile din lume, fie ele prietene sau str<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span>ine. At<text:span text:style-name="T5">â</text:span>t de aprins trebuie s<text:span text:style-name="T5">ã</text:span> fie focul dragostei <text:span text:style-name="T5">º</text:span>i